description: This file defines a React component named AddressForm used for collecting delivery address information in a food delivery frontend application. It includes TypeScript types for Address data and component props, and renders a form with input fields for address details.

methods.name: AddressForm
methods.description: A React functional component that renders an address form with input fields for full name, address lines, city, state, postal code, phone, and instructions. It manages value updates via onChange callback.
